  "slide": 13,
  "duration": 38.42,
  "text": "The proposal is we co-build and you own this. We work with your teams to make work flows and build what fits your operations. We will complement your deep food safety expertise and provide scalable architecture and a responsive team that understands what is at stake, what it means for records to be available every time. And crucially, what we build together is EcoWise's IP. The platform and intellectual property remain yours, protecting your competitive advantage as we go forward.",
